OL,5, Alice Thompson wanted to work shorter  
OL,6, hours to pick her daughter up from     
OL,7, nursery, but ended up resigning.       
OL,9,FThe former estate agent spent tens of  
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds pursuing the case  
OL,11,Fagainst her former employer.           
OL,13,FShe was awarded #185,000 by an         
OL,14,Femployment tribunal and this week told 
OL,15,Fthe BBC it was "a long, exhausting     
OL,16,Fjourney".                              
OL,18,FThe tribunal ruled she had suffered    
OL,19,Findirect sex discrimination when the   
OL,20,Ffirm refused to consider her request.  
